race.comment: EIDETIC MEMORY (1) slotted in just off the lead from the wide draw last start and boxed on to finish second (30.11) at this track in a Grade 5 over 520m. Can measure up this time. WOOTOWN WILL (2) turned in a moderate performance last time when fifth at this track over 520m behind Hard Style Girl (30.39) in a Grade 4/5. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and three minor placings to his credit. Worth following up. TOMMY TANGLES (8) clocked a swift 29.94 when winning over 520m at this track last start. Rates a leading chance if runs up to latest. ON THE RAZZLE (3) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can make amends.
